content:
NavigatedEventHandler Delegate

Definition

Represents the method that will handle Navigated events.

In this Article

public delegate void NavigatedEventHandler(object sender, NavigationEventArgs e);
Inheritance
Object
System.Delegate
NavigatedEventHandler

Remarks

This event handler is used for the following events:

  • System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigated
  • System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigated
  • System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigated
  • System.Windows.Application.Navigated
